OpenquickIT is a extensible IT control panel, for Linux servers.

It can run standalone, or manage multiple remote servers.

It will help you in easy deployment and manteinance of servers, and to
consolidate your network services, generate reports, alerts, backups, and
lot of other features that IT people needs.

OpenquickIT management interface, is build over the Catalyst web framework,
so you can use the Comprehensive Perl Archive Network (CPAN), to extend
this application to your needs.

For installation instructions, see INSTALL.

For more information:http://wiki.github.com/poisonbit/OpenquickIT
